data.description: Nicely updated home right near the school! New flooring, roof 3.5 years old. All appliances less than 4 years old and fridge conveys. New ceramic tile floors  in kitchen and bathrooms and new tile backsplash. Huge, gorgeous, level backyard, completely fenced. Septic has been inspected and there is a new pump. 3 tier septic and lines are in front yard to keep lawn nice! Home warranty offered! Call listing agent today!
